---
title: Lock-free MVCC reads (ADR-0064)
---
flowchart TB
  W["Writer"]
  NEW["Build new overlay<br/>(pages + tombstones)"]
  SWAP["arc-swap<br/>(atomic publish)"]
  SNAP["Immutable snapshot"]
  R1["Reader A (old snapshot)"]
  R2["Reader B (new snapshot)"]
  W --> NEW --> SWAP --> SNAP
  SNAP --> R2
  SWAP -. old snapshot freed<br/>when last reader drops .-> R1
